name: Square sterling silver studs
description: These small square studs are cast in sterling silver and given a brushed finish.

name: Sterling silver chrysanthemum necklace
description:
This botanical themed pendant is cast in sterling silver and given a brushed finish for extra sparkle.
The chrysanthemum is 3cm wide and 3cm long. It hangs from a 45cm sterling silver snake chain that is made in Italy.

name: Cupped flower necklace
description:
This cupped flower pendant is cast in sterling silver and hangs from a 45cm Italian made sterling silver snake chain.
The actual flower is 1.5cm in diameter.

name: Ottoman necklace with charms
description:
This necklace comprises of a pendant that is inspired by the beautiful pattern design featured on ceramic ottoman tiles. It is cast in sterling silver and hangs alongside a delicate seed pearl and crystal.
The pendant is 3.5cm and are 2cm wide.
The sterling silver snake chain is 45cm long and made in Italy.

name: Ruched body dress
description:
This dress is made in a soft cotton jersey and drapes in all the right places. It is a "free size" garment that fits up to a size 14.
It is shown on a size 10 mannequin.

name: Merino wool scarf (emerald and indigo)
description:
This hand painted scarf is made from a soft merino wool jersey.
The water based dyes used mean we can paint on the fabric in the same way one would brush watercolours onto canvas.

The scarf measures 190cm long and 50cm wide.
Please keep in mind the nature of handpainting means no two scarves are alike.

name: Charcoal grey scarf with porcelain button
description:
This charcoal grey neck warmer is hand knitted with a pure wool yarn and lined with a wool/cashmere blend to keep you warm and snug.
It is finished with an oversized porcelain button. 

Due to the nature of materials used this necklet must be hand washed with warm water or dry cleaned.

Within Australia we use Express Post which is a trackable service that can be followed on the Australia Post website.

name: Silver twig earring
description:
Made from sterling silver, these modern earrings will make a bold statement.
They are just over 7cms long. 
The brushed silver finish catches the light and adds an extra element to this earring.

Free shipping within Australia

name: Oval drop earring
description:
These sterling silver earrings have been given a brushed finish.
The oval is just under 1.5cm long and 1.2cm wide. It hangs close to the lobe making it a stylish and easy to wear everyday earring. The earring, including hook, is 3.5 cms long.

Free shipping within Australia

name: Silver halo studs
description:
These small ring shaped studs are perfect for every day wear.
They are cast from sterling silver and given a brushed finish.
The circles measure 1.5cm in diameter.

Free shipping within Australia

name: Ottoman Earrings
description:
These earrings are cast in sterling silver and take inspiration from the beautiful pattern design featured on ceramic ottoman tiles.
They hang 3.5cm and are 2cm wide.

Free shipping within Australia

name: Japanese fan earrings
description:
These fan shaped earrings are cast in sterling silver and have a lovely matt finish.
They incorporate the traditional Japanese wave pattern known as  Seikai-ha.
Including hook, they are almost 5cm long and 3.5cm wide.

Free shipping within Australia

name: Geometric disc earring
description:
These drop style earrings are made from sterling silver and given a matt finish.
The fine internal cuts create a striking geometric pattern.
They are 2.4cm in diameter.

Free shipping within Australia

name: Intertwined ring necklace
description:
This necklace is made up of three intertwined rings inspired by Russian wedding bands.
Ring 1: sterling silver dipped in rose gold
Ring 2: sterling silver dipped in yellow gold
Ring 3: sterling silver
The pendant hangs from a long (83cms) sterling silver snake chain.

Free shipping within Australia

name: Pentagon earrings
description:
Is this a polygon or a pentagon? 
I'm not sure but am sure that these earrings are cast from sterling silver and sandblasted to a soft lustre.
The form is hollow making the earring light and easy on the earlobe.
Free shipping within Australia.

name: Double circle drop earring
description:
These sterling silver earrings comprise of one black oxidized circle and a brush finished circle. The contrasting finishes give this geometric  earring an elegant and modern look.
This item includes free shipping within Australia.

name: Pebble earring
description:
These small pebbles are formed from a high fired porcelain and finished with a glossy glaze.
The hang from 20mm sterling silver hoops made from a .8mm sterling silver wire. A small beaten silver star sits in front of the pebble.
This item comes with free postage within Australia.

name: Silk tassel earring
description:
These tassel earrings are crafted from sterling silver and silk.
The disc component has been given a hammered finish.
They are 6cm long. 
This item comes with free postage within Australia.

description:

The dress ties in the front and back, panels have been made wide so the garment wraps and overlaps so as not to expose the wearer.
It is a free size garment and works from a size 10 to 16.
This is a versatile dress that works equally well with a tee, fine knit top or collared shirt.

Here it is shown on a size 10

name: Ruffle dress
description:
This tunic style dress with a shoulder ruffle works with leggings, pants or jeans for a more casual look.
This one size dress works on a size 10 to 12.
You will need to wear a tee or tank top under this dress because of its wide neckline.

Grey pin stripe: cotton poly
Navy: linen viscose
Grey: cotton spandex
 


Free shipping within Australia

name: Tail tee
description:
These striped tees are made with a soft cotton/spandex jersey.
They are one size and shown here on a size 10 but because of the relaxed fit work equally well on a size 12. 
The sleeve and bottom have been left unhemmed but will not fray.

We offer free delivery with this product within Australia.

name: silk necklaces
description:
Long silk necklace with brushed sterling silver crescent.
The necklace is finished with faceted silver beads and comes in four different colours.

name: Hammered disc earring with free shipping
description:
These earrings consist of two sterling silver discs that have been hammered, oxidized and polished to give them a beautifully weathered patina. The larger disc has a diameter of 35mm
They hang from 35mm sterling hoops made from a 0.8mm silver wire.

name: Bangle with beads
description:
Sterling silver bangle with porcelain beads and a cupped silver disc.
The bangle is made from 2mm silver wire and given a irregular hammed finish. The stained porcelain beads are burnished to a soft satin finish.
This bangle can be worn alone or stacked with other bangles.

Internal dimensions are:
Bangle 1= 66mm (medium)
Bangle 2= 65mm (medium)
Bangle 3= 62mm (small)
Bangle 4= 63mm (small)

name: Drop waist tunic dress
description:
This tunic style dress with a drop waist and funnel neck collar comes in a relaxed size 12 (Australian sizing).
It can be worn with or without the waist tie and features 2 small pleats in the front and back of the skirt.

name: Slouch top
description:
The slouch tee is one of those tops that is easy to wear and can be thrown over almost anything. An effortless way to look smart and feel comfortable.
This "free size" garment is shown on a size 10 but works equally well up to a size 14.

They are made from a light weight Japanese cotton voile.

name: Porcelain & silver cupped necklace
description:
This delicate necklace incorporates a silver cup that nests within a larger cupped piece of porcelain.
It hangs on a 45cm sterling silver snake chain.
The second photo shows the complete colour range.
Charcoal, Teal, Pale Blue, Brown and Bright Blue.

name: Double porcelain pendant necklace
description:
Two high fired porcelain pendants hanging from a 55cm sterling ball or  45cm (18 inch) snake chain.
One pendant is embossed with a animal design and painted in a contrasting colour and the the other is finished with a delicate pattern that fuses to the surface and is completely scratch resistant.
The clay body is colour stained and left unglazed leaving a pebble like surface.

Please note: these are all one-off pieces and this is the actual necklace you will receive.


Please specify your choose of chain in the comments section.

name: Animal Pendant Necklace
description:
These animal shapes are stripped back to there most basic form.
They are cut from stainless steel and given a smooth brushed finish.
The pendant hangs from a 45cm (17 inch) sterling silver snake chain.

name: Triple stacking rings
description:
Three sterling silver stacking rings that can be worn together or separately.
Each ring has been given a different finish, matt brushed silver, oxidised silver and high polished.

These rings are available in 3 sizes.
Small (Aus & British = L1/2) (US = 6)
Med (Aus & British = N1/2) (US = 7)
Large (Aus & British = P1/2) (US = 8)

name: Charcoal porcelain disc earring
description:
The disc component of these earrings are made from a dark charcoal stained porcelain.
They have been hand sanded and feel very smooth to touch.
The underglaze design has been fired on at 1280 degrees and will not fade or scratch.
We make our earring hooks from a .9mm sterling silver wire and the safety catch on the bottom makes them tricky to lose.
The sterling silver tube at the front and back of the earrings hold them securely in their place.
These earrings hang 4cm (1.6inches) from your ear lobe and only weigh 3.6 grams, so they are very easy to wear.
 
We have chosen three of our most popular designs to make available to our online customers, white flowers, black swirl and Asa No Ha (japanese geometric line pattern).

Due to the hand made nature of this product there may be slight variations in colour shape and pattern.

name: Brown porcelain disc earrings
description:
The disc component of these earrings are made from a warm brown stained porcelain.
They have been hand sanded and feel very smooth to touch.
The underglaze design has been fired on at 1280 degrees and will not fade or scratch.
We make our earring hooks from a .9mm sterling silver wire and the safety catch on the bottom makes them tricky to lose.
The sterling silver tube at the front and back of the earrings keep them nicely in their place.
These earrings hang 4cm (1.6inches) from your ear lobe and only weigh 3.6 grams, so they are very easy to wear.
 
We have chosen three of our most popular designs to make available to our online customers, Black swirl, Fine vines and Dog flower.

Due to the hand made nature of this product there may be slight variations in colour shape and pattern.

name: Pod Earring
description:
These delicate pod like forms are cast from silver and attached to a .9mm wide sterling silver ear hook.
They are available in either the black oxidised with polished silver edges or bright silver.

name: Cylinder necklace
description: This cylinder necklace,made from sterling silver, has a very architectural feel to it. It hangs from a 16 inch (42 cm) snake chain with a 1mm diameter. This necklace is delicate, Contemporary and very easy to wear.

name: Hammered Rectangle Earrings
description:
These Hammered sterling silver earrings make quite a statement but are remarkably easy to wear.
They hang 6.5 cm (2.6 inches).
The hammering process creates two slightly irregular earrings, as shown in the second photo, but we believe it only adds to their charm.

name: Pebble necklace on Suede
description:
This necklace is made from our stained, hand rolled and burnished porcelain beads.
It incorporates pieces of hammered and brushed sterling silver.
The use of suede cord allows it to be worn at various lengths.

All our pebble necklaces are one offs so the composition is always unique. The shown piece is the item you will receive.

name: Sterling silver bangle with urchin charm
description:
This bangle is forged from 4mm sterling silver. It is solid and weighs 19.5 grams.

It features a silver urchin charm that moves freely on the bangle.

The inside diameter is 66mm, making it a medium size.

name: 13 bead necklace
description:
This necklace is made up of 13 sterling silver beads polished to a luxurious finish.
It hangs from a delicate 42cm trace chain.

Available in Matt silver and Gold vermeil.
Gold vermeil is a micron hard gold plate over sterling silver.

name: Silver seed pearl necklace
description:
This neckalace comes in 4 versions.
An owl, seahorse, bird and an Indian mandala.
They are all cast in sterling silver and polished to a soft matt finish.
A tiny seed pearl hangs alongside each pendant.
They hang from a 45cm sterling silver ball chain.

name: 3 square necklace
description:
This necklace is made up of 3 hammered sterling silver squares hanging from a delicate 42cm trace chain.
The square are silver, gold vermeil and rose gold vermeil.
Gold & rose gold vermeil are micron hard gold plating over sterling silver.

name: Hammered square earring
description:
These hammered square earrings are made from sterling silver and polished to a shiny finish.
Available in bright silver and gold vermeil.
Gold vermeil is a micron hard gold plating over sterling silver.

name: Donut Disc necklace
description:
This delicate sterling silver disc is polished to a mirror finish.
It hangs from a 45cm (18inch) sterling silver ball chain.

name: Large donut disc necklace

name: Cupped stud earring

name: Triangle stud

name: Hammered circle earing

name: Sterling silver oval studs

name: Sterling silver & waxed cotton bracelet
description:
These colourful bracelets are made with a hammered sterling silver disc and strung on a waxed cotton cord.

The cord is adustable and works on all size wrists.

It comes in black, pink, orange, blue, purple and brown.

This item comes with free standard postage within Australia.

name: Cupped heart necklace.
description:
This delicate sterling silver heart has a brushed finish and lovely cupped form.
It hangs from a 45cm (18inch) sterling silver ball chain.
